# Project: AI Product Owner Multi-Agent System

## What This Project Does
A multi-agent AI system that takes Slack messages and meeting notes as input,
orchestrates a Product Owner agent and a Tech Lead agent to analyze requirements,
then automatically generates user stories, assigns them to developers, and
evaluates its own performance using a dedicated Evaluator Agent.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3.11+
- CrewAI for multi-agent orchestration
- OpenAI GPT-4.1-nano as the LLM
- Streamlit for frontend UI
- python-dotenv for environment variables

## Project Structure
```
